comment: Johnny Depp knew Hunter S. Thompson. When Hunter shot himself, Depp searched around and found Â his old novel rejected multiple times. After seeing the movie, it is no mystery it was rejected way back when. It is like reminiscing about my early 20s. Of course, I might change the title to Tequila Diary, the 487 proof rum would be JP5 jet fuel and Puerto Rico would be either Tijuana, Singapore, or Olongapo City in the Philipines.
